                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-236-off1210 t18280911-236-cd1211"></join>, 1 mat, value 2s.; 1 bag, value 2s.: 1 rasp, value 6d.; 3 nail-bags, value 1s. 6d.; 1 screw-driver, value 3d., and 1 file, value 1s. 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
