                     <interp inst="t18280911-236-person1342" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . He did say so; I said I would not advise him to do anything.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280911-236-person1343">
                  WILLIAM 
                  GRANT
               <interp inst="t18280911-236-person1343" type="surname" value="GRANT"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280911-236-person1343" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280911-236-person1343" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             re-examined. Q. What was the right thing to do with that mat? A. To take it to an out-house, where we keep such things - we use them in packing, but not very often; the prisoner had been three or four years in our employ, and had a good character.</p>
